item.title: Dump #344
item.description:
1 Hey, y’all! I’m Ashleigh (They/Them) and I share memes sometimes.
2 I’m in Minneapolis this weekend and curating this dump for my fellow degenerates!
3 Daylight savings + traveling = me, dead but delicious.
4 As a treat.
5 Alhamdulillah!
6
7 I don’t care if they leave.
8 It’s pretty rare that I am intentionally mean, but I am SO good at it that folks are shocked.
9 Memes = Art (Sorry, Not Sorry) If you don’t want to see political memes (totes understandable), you can feel free to mute my account.
10 Look, I get that it’s a lot. You don’t have to be aware of it 24/7. We all need breaks from it. Please remember, having the option to “take a break” is a privilege.
11 Mmhm
12 When someone enters the “spending time together socially” phase of friendship.
13 The golden rule, bruh.
14
15 Be not afraid. Or do. Whatever. I don’t make the rules.
16
17 So hot *bites lip*
18 Fair.
19 *chef’s kiss*
20
21 Thank goodness.
22 I Want To Leave.
23 Wait, actually I want to stay.
24 Hhnngh *bites lip* The yearning. The punishment. The stimulation. The denial.
25 All the time. I think it’s why I make such delicious potato-based dishes.
26 *Wet Macaroni Noises* *Harmonica Noises* *Vibraslap Noises*
27 Like you do.
28 Yearning level: catastrophic
29 I mean I’m trying to get SOMETHING in my guts. Also: https://youtu.be/dIk8VDcO5is?si=OwLWTOQUSjOT0IJa This song has been on repeat since the album dropped.
30 Actually, Ashnikko’s new album could explain my recent rise in yearning.
31 This may also be a factor. Also: it just feels so gooooood.
32 And so is my Hitachi (Heyooooo).
33 So sowwy.
34 Oh, you mean my ex?
35 Imagine having all this and fumbling me?!? To be fair, we were not a good match, but still.
36 And now I am super happy with my partner. It’s truly possible to feel safe and be happy in a relationship.
37 See #36 I mean I cannot recommend self-work/psychotherapy/curiosity about yourself enough. How can you know what you want (and ask for it) if you don’t know who/why/how you are ?
38 Nah, “he” saw it. He gave me snaps.
39 #
40 Look,the horrors (and chores) persist, but so do I.
41 It really is.
42 Recent therapy journey stuff.
43
44
45
46
47 Which is actually like so much less drama, tbh.
48
49 It’s never too late to work on yourself. The time will pass anyway.
50 Take care of yourselves and each other. Byeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee!

item.title: Let's send food to people in need!
item.description:
MrPuckett is out today proposing to his girlfriend, so it's a long time Angel and first time OP running the show today! If you'd like to help a struggling Imgurian get groceries or a meal today there are 2 easy ways -
You can find a request for food in the comments, reply to them and then send a DM to get an order set up Or you can contribute to the Imgurian Meal Fund and we'll send the food for you!
Anonymous Angels have been such an amazing help for us to feed more people, we love you so much! https://www.paypal.me/TheFreePizzaDude https://ko-fi.com/thefreepizzadude
And here's how you'd send it yourself! Any questions as an Angel? Just shoot us a message! We'll be on this username until 6pm central
HelaSisterOfThor's cat is here to show you how it works for requests -
It's much easier for us to help requests in the US but we'll do our best to pick up requests from any country. Putting your country in your comment helps us match you to an Angel in your area
Any questions as a requestor? Just leave a comment! We'll have helpers on the post for 6 hours
16,083 meals since we started 1,161 grocery orders sent 6 more hours to help as many people as we can Let's get it going! ... With a first time OP for today's post, please forgive us for any delays!
